		REPLACE cur_Deta_View.pDtoCli2 	WITH lnPDtoCli2 ADDITIVE
		REPLACE cur_Deta_View.pDtoCli3 	WITH lnPDtoCli3 ADDITIVE
		REPLACE cur_Deta_View.pDtoCli4 	WITH lnPDtoCli4 ADDITIVE
